#: templates/dashboard/home.html:20
msgid ""
"\n"
"          Programme National de Lutte contre la Trypanosomiase Humaine "
"Africaine (PNLTHA) of the DRC Ministry of Health drives the programme to "
"diagnose, treat and reduce HAT cases in the DRC.\n"
"          "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Republique Democratique du Congo, Ministere de la Santé Publique, Programme "
"National de Lutte contre la THA (PNLTHA)."

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:31
msgid "Map showing pilot health zones"
msgstr "Carte montrant les zones de santé pilotes"

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:34
msgid "Programme Mission"
msgstr "Mission du Programme"

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:36
msgid ""
"\n"
"        To coordinate and organise the strugge against HAT in RD Congo\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Coordonner et Organiser la lutte contre la THA en R.D.Congo"

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:40
msgid "Programme Objective"
msgstr "Objectif du Programme"

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:42
msgid ""
"\n"
"        To reduce the morbidity and mortality due to HAT to a level "
"compatible with a normal productive life for the inhabitants of areas where "
"the disease is endemic (1 case per 10,000 inhabitants)\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Réduire la morbidité et la mortalité due au THA à un niveau compatible avec "
"une vie productive normale pour les habitants des zones où la maladie est "
"endémique (1 cas par 10000 habitants)"

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:46
msgid "Programme Organisation"
msgstr "Organisation du Programme"

#: templates/dashboard/home.html:48
